<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id56b223b3-2930-11f1-a4c1-c531e6569a02" identifier="/us/usc/t14/s1926"><num value="1926">§ 1926.</num><heading> Cadet applicants; preappointment travel to Academy</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary is authorized to expend appropriated funds for selective preappointment travel to the Academy for orientation visits of cadet applicants.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id56b223b4-2930-11f1-a4c1-c531e6569a02">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/98/557/s24/a">Pub. L. 98–557, § 24(a)</ref>, <date date="1984-10-30">Oct. 30, 1984</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/98/2872">98 Stat. 2872</ref>, § 181a; renumbered § 1926, <ref href="/us/pl/115/282/tI/s110/b">Pub. L. 115–282, title I, § 110(b)</ref>, <date date="2018-12-04">Dec. 4, 2018</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/132/4212">132 Stat. 4212</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
